户端完全缺失，`ExternalMatchReceived` 为死代码\n\n**问题描述**\n- `apps/mobile/p
ubspec.yaml` 声明了 `socket_io_client: ^3.0.1`，但整个 `apps/mobile/lib/` 代码库
