，或在外部通过 event 携带。\n  3. 示例：\n     void _onMatchModalDismissed(..., 
Emitter<MatchingState> emit) {\n       final prev = state; // 需要保存 previous 
state 的引用\n       if (prev is MatchingMatchCreated && prev.previousState is M
atchingLoadSuccess) {\n         emit(prev.previousState);\n       } else if (pre
v is MatchingMatchCreated && prev.previousState is MatchingLoadEmpty) {\n       
 emit(prev.previousState);\n       }\n     }\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. API 契约不一
致：`avatar_url` 在 OpenAPI/Dart 客户端中为 required，后端却可能省略\n\n**问题描
述**\n- `docs/api-contracts/matching.yaml` 中 `RecommendationCard` 的 `required`
