atchedUser?.nickname ?? \'\',\n      \'avatar_url\': response.data.matchedUser?.
avatarUrl,\n    },\n  }));\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. HomePage 重复实现了 SwipeCardSt
ack 逻辑，design-system 组件未被使用\n\n**问题描述**\n- `packages/design-system/
lib/src/organisms/swipe_card_stack.dart` 已经实现了完整的卡片堆叠、手势、动画逻
辑。\n- `apps/mobile/lib/presentation/pages/home_page.dart` 却内嵌了一个私有 `_C
ardStackArea` StatefulWidget，逻辑与 `SwipeCardStack` 几乎完全一致（手势阈值、动
